# Netlify/Vercel HTTP Headers Configuration

This file defines custom headers for deployment platforms supporting _headers file format.

```
/*
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'

/feed.xml
  Content-Type: application/rss+xml

/*.json
  Content-Type: application/json
```

See your deployment platform's documentation for details on header configuration.
